    "941:207": "abhidhyā priyarūpeṇa hanti kāmātmakaṃ jagat|",
    "941:208": "arirmitramukheneva priyavākkaluṣāśayaḥ||46||",
    "941:209": "daurmanasyābhidhānastu pratigho viṣayāśritaḥ|",
    "941:210": "mohādyenānuvṛtena paratreha ca hanyate||47||",
    "941:211": "anurodhavirodhābhyāṃ śitoṣṇābhyāmivārditaḥ|",
    "941:212": "śarma nāpnoti na śreyaścalendriyamato jagat||48||",
    "941:213": "nendriyaṃ viṣaye tāvat pravṛttamapi sajjate|",
    "941:214": "yāvanna manasastatra parikalpaḥ pravartate||49||",
    "941:215": "indhane sati vāyau ca yathā jvalati pāvakaḥ|",
    "941:216": "viṣayāt parikalpācca kleśāgnirjāyate tathā||50||",
    "941:217": "abhūtaparikalpena viṣayasya hi vadhyate|",
    "941:218": "tameva viṣayaṃ paśyan bhūtataḥ parimucyate||51||",
    "941:219": "dṛṣṭvaikaṃ rūpamanyo hi rajyate'nyaḥ praduṣyati|",
    "941:220": "kaścid bhavati madhyasthastatraivānyo ghṛṇāyate||52||",
    "941:221": "ato na viṣayo heturbandhāya na vimuktaye|",
    "941:222": "parikalpaviśeṣeṇa saṃgo bhavati vā na vā||53||",
    "941:223": "kāryaḥ paramayatnena tasmādindriyasaṃvaraḥ|",
    "941:224": "indriyāṇi hyagutpāni duḥkhāya ca bhavāya ca||54||",
    "941:225": "kāmabhogabhogavadbhirātmadṛṣṭidṛṣṭibhiḥ pramādanaikamūrddhabhiḥ praharṣalolajivhakaiḥ|",
    "941:226": "indriyoragairmanobilaśrayaiḥ spṛhāviṣaiḥ śamāgadādṛte na dṛṣṭamasti yaccikitset||55||",
    "941:227": "tasmādeṣāmakuśalakarāṇāmarīṇāṃ cakṣurghrāṇaśravaṇarasanasparśanānām|",
    "941:228": "sarvāvasthaṃ bhava viniyamādapramatto māsminnarthe kṣaṇamapi kṛthāstvaṃ pramādam||56||",
    "941:229": "saundarananda mahākāvye “śīla evaṃ indriya-saṃyama“ nāma trayodaśa sarga samāpta|"
}